snippet.title: Checkout my next indie game project, Elevator Warp | Devlog
snippet.description:
Elevator Warp is a new game of mine, that will be participating in the upcoming June 2024 Steam Next Fest.

Your goal is simple. Take the elevator to floor 6. But this is no ordinary elevator... Who knows which random floor you'll end up at. A hotel, dungeon, hedge maze, a train? Check the clues on each floor to be able to progress, and achieve the perfect run!

- Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2803900/Elevator_Warp/
- Discord: discord.gg/tv9XvXB5n6
- Website: https://alittlemoregames.com.au/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/LittleMoreGames
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/alittlemoregames/
- Email: alittlemoregames@gmail.com
